      "content": "okay honestly that makes me feel better. since you said it's unlikely to be an issue, do you think it's actually better to take them together? like, if i take the wine and the pill at the same time, will that help me stay asleep longer through the night? i just want to make sure i'm doing it the most effective way so i don't wake up at 3am again.",
